753
00:29:59,614 --> 00:30:00,615
SEAN: Right?

754
00:30:01,749 --> 00:30:03,449
Mmm.

755
00:30:03,451 --> 00:30:04,720
Wanna try some?

756
00:30:05,086 --> 00:30:06,421
Great.

